unittitle_ssm: Kenneth Silverman Research Collection on Samuel F. B. Morse
abstract_ssm: This collection contains research materials collected by Kenneth Silverman while working on his book Lightning Man: The Accursed Life of Samuel F.B. Morse. Materials include photocopied articles and essays, microfilm, and correspondence (mostly transcribed) dating from 1792 to 1892. This collection does not include original materials from Morse.
title_ssm: Lightning Man: The Accursed Life of Samuel F.B. Morse.
The Life and Times of Cotton Mather,
The Miracle on Washington Square: New York University.
